	<h1>Stephen J. Beck</h1>
	<p>Steve Beck sits on the Executive Board of Directors for Showcall Inc. He provides strategic, financial and business planning as well as business development opportunities. Beck currently also serves as the president and executive director of the Military Bowl. the president of Five Star Basketball of Greater Washington, and is the president and founder of the Five Star Foundation which provides grants that allow underprivileged kids to attend Five Star Basketball camps. From 1998 to 2002 Steve served as vice president of Sports America and assisted in producing the McDonald’s All-American game. Beck’s event experience spans three decades, as his involvement in the sports industry has always contained an event component. Steve lives in Montgomery County Maryland with his wife and four children.</p>
