	<h1>Mary Beck</h1>
	<p>Mary Beck brings a variety of work experiences to Showcall in the areas of government relations, marketing and contract administration. Mary spent almost 12 years in the Biotechnology Industry (Seikagaku America, BIOCON and Integra BioSciences) and spent a number of years developing creative marketing and advertising strategies, while traveling the world.</p>
