	<p>Mark brings 27 years experience in the areas of information technology management and video production.</p>
	<p>Mark's career includes positions as a security analyst with the US Navy; networking management for the US Postal Service and US Department of Justice; eCommerce project management for Coca-Cola; eCommerce marketing management for IBM and KPMG; and Deputy CSO for the world's largest manaufacturer of magnetic card stripe readers. In addition to his technological background, Mark has worked on over 20 feature films and broadcast television series as a production designer, art director, propmaster, set decorator and stills photographer. Mark's live event production resume includes the Pittsburgh G20 in 2009 and the APEC Summit in 2011. He is skilled in video editing software such as Avid and Final Cut Pro.</p>
